[In response to the request for information for the encephalitis cases reported in ProMED-mail archive no. 20130401.1613261, Prof. Be-Nazir Ahmed provided the statement below. - Mod.TY]:

Yesterday [1 Apr 2013], we got the laboratory report identifying Nipah virus infection.

--
Prof. Be-Nazir Ahmed MBBS MPH MPhil
